*numeric-24.2-r2 (12 Oct 2006)

  12 Oct 2006; Sebastien Fabbro <seb@ist.utl.pt>:
  +numeric-24.2-r2.ebuild
  +files/numeric-lapack.patch
  +files/numeric-umath.patch	
  Fixed an include placement for math.h, allowing acosh and asinh.
  Fixed lapack implementation, no more atlas dependent.

	
*numeric-24.2-r1 (06 Jun 2006)

  06 Jun 2006; Sebastien Fabbro <seb@ist.utl.pt>:
  +files/numeric-arrayobject.patch, +files/numeric-lapack.patch,
  +numeric-24.2-r1.ebuild. 
  Import from main tree. Fixed a memory leak, and added the possibility
  to compile linear algebra with installed blas/cblas/lapack.
  Tested against gcc41 and gcc34 on amd64, x86. Added longdescription
  in metadata.xml. Closes bugs #81520 and #114885.
  
